# ─── CDK / AWS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# `cdk.out*` catches the per-stage variants `cdk deploy --app "python
# app_staging.py"` produces (cdk.out.staging/, cdk.out.company/, …)
# in addition to the default `cdk.out/`. These are CFN synth artifacts
# and the layer asset zips — never check them in.
cdk.out/
cdk.out.*/
.aws-sam/
*.zip

