# ─── Local scratch / Dev utilities ───────────────────────────────────────────
# `scratch/`, `tmp/`, and `.local/` are conventional places for dev-only
# experiments, throwaway scripts, and per-developer notes that should
# never reach the repo. Add new dev artifacts under one of these
# instead of inventing fresh top-level folders.
scratch/
tmp/
.local/
*.bak
*.orig

# ─── Logs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
logs/
